{"tid":1261260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊send email攞灰狗更表！","createTime":"2019-06-27T06:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T06:52:15.000Z","uid":268905,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f34c7dbea2673e9f9c2c33a4ef1e9c11bf6d3dd7","tid":1261260,"uid":268905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:48:51.000Z","msg":"起到條友英文全名未？<br />\n<br />\n大家可以send email/填form去警務處公開資料主任度攞灰狗更表，睇下佢26-27號番咩更。<br />\n<br />\n公務員朋友話有全名就可以問，因為更表係pre-exiting document，佢地無得懶Admin burden，10日內要回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.access.gov.hk/tc/howtomakeinfo/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.access.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fhowtomakeinfo%2Findex.html&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0doVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=28243df3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.access.gov.hk/tc/howtomakeinfo/index.html</a> <br />\n揀番警務處就有email address<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1586e2a229ed52cdbafdd563d35161c61f5cc939","tid":1261260,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:50:00.000Z","msg":"兩個字？"},{"pid":"aae42457e194a5a3644abeffe561e428e3460e02","tid":1261260,"uid":33101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:51:52.000Z","msg":"張X OR X淼???"},{"pid":"99220035621405b399d48af825bca86facd3977a","tid":1261260,"uid":268905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1586e2a229ed52cdbafdd563d35161c61f5cc939","tid":1261260,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:50:00.000Z","msg":"兩個字？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:52:15.000Z","msg":"Facebook 叫Sum Cheung <br />\n有無人搵到其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/